description:
This is a 11 minute workout called '10 Minute Guided Meditation for Focus' from the channel Declutter The Mind.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation and Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: In this 10 min guided meditation, you'll use mindfulness and the focus on the breath to help increase your concentration and clairty for work, school, and general productivity. In 10 minutes, practice your attention to help clear the mind of distraction and gain laser like focus. This guided meditation is without music, and is voice only.
